From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Dynamic Devices <support@dynamicdevices.co.uk>
Date: Sun, 1 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] imx9/scmi: always export check_secondary_cnt_set

image-container.c calls check_secondary_cnt_set for all i.MX9 SCMI SPL
builds, but the symbol lived under #ifdef CONFIG_IMX95 in soc.c. Factory
u-boot-fio SPL then fails to link when that ifdef is false in scmi/soc.o
while callers remain. Export the stub whenever scmi/soc.c is built.
---
 arch/arm/mach-imx/imx9/scmi/soc.c | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

--- a/arch/arm/mach-imx/imx9/scmi/soc.c	2026-06-01 09:51:50.912963575 +0100
+++ b/arch/arm/mach-imx/imx9/scmi/soc.c	2026-06-01 09:51:50.912963575 +0100
@@ -1595,6 +1595,7 @@
 {
 	return is_imx95_a0() ? 0x400: 0x4000;
 }
+#endif
 
 bool check_secondary_cnt_set(unsigned long *set_off)
 {
@@ -1603,4 +1604,3 @@
 
 	return false;
 }
-#endif
